%h1 Organizations

- if @organizations.present?
  Choose an organization, or #{link_to 'create a new one', new_organization_path}:

  %ul
  - @organizations.each do |organization|
    %li
      %b= organization.name
      = link_to 'select', select_organization_path(organization.id)
      |
      = link_to 'show', organization_path(organization.id)
- else
  To start using Watchfire you must create an Organization.

  %br

  = render 'form'
